ns15:Method.description: Enables a client system to create a safety report record in the Safety Reporting System with all fields required for safety report creation.
ns15:Method.name: initiateSafetyReport

ns15:Method.description: Provides the capability to associate adverse events to a safety report.
ns15:Method.name: associateAdverseEventsToSafetyReport

ns15:Method.description: Provides the capability to dissociate an adverse event from a safety report.
ns15:Method.name: dissociateAdverseEventsFromSafetyReport

ns15:Method.description: Provides the capability to update the adverse event information in the safety report.
ns15:Method.name: updateAdverseEventInformationInSafetyReport
